.. _Changelog:

Changelog for snf-vncauthproxy
^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^

.. _Changelog-1.7:

v1.7
====

Released: UNRELEASED

	* Remove distribute setup dependency
	* Add compatibility with gevent >= 1.0

.. _Changelog-1.6:

v1.6rc2
=======

Released: UNRELEASED

	* Add the ``--proxy-listen-address`` command line option and update the
	  JSON response to include the ``proxy_address`` key, which specifies where
	  vncauthproxy will listen to for incoming client connections.

v1.6rc1
=======

Released: Thu Sep 25 15:20:45 EEST 2014

	* Add support for WebSockets

.. _Changelog-1.5:

v1.5
====

Released: Mon Jun 23 11:51:43 EEST 2014

	* Add Changelog, README and docs
	* Replace Unix domain control sockets with TCP control sockets, with
	  basic authentication and SSL support.
	* Add the vncauthproxy-passwd tool to manage the users file.
